Job Description
Momin Solutions is hiring Telesales Resources on urgent basis. We need telesales representative who may introduce our business in all over the United Kingdom. Job involves outbound calls to our clients and customers in London and other areas of United Kingdom. Candidate also have to receive inbound calls from our customers and clients to entertain them with best of our services. Candidate should have at least one year experience of outbound calling in a B2B campaign.
Job Specification
Verbal Communication, Phone Skills, Listening, Data Entry Skills, People Skills, Informing, Customer Focus, Customer Service, Attention to Detail, Professionalism, Multi-tasking
